data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED...$5K Bonus to Buyers toward closing costs or interest rate buy down.Bonuses Apply with contract by February 14thDon't miss out on this cozy, 3 bedroom Plus DEN, recently updated, Ocean Access home.  This home sits in the heart of Palm city & only minutes from the inlet & restaurants in this family friendly community of Rustic Hills!   This home had a FULL remodel including roof, AC, windows, flooring, bathrooms kitchen & floor throughout. The kitchen offers Granite & Quartz tops & newer appliances. (The open floor plan makes it easy for entertaining and both sets of french doors from den and primary bedroom lead to 30 ft wide covered patio & 38 ft dock. The backyard makes for a great place to watch beautiful sun rises/sets. Dock, 10K boat lift & landscape wall were installed in 2023 to include plumbing and electric to dock as well as all new irrigation system in the back yard.
